These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel, crime
1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | crime | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, bus
1. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the bus##2
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Transport   | bus | jet-ski | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, basketball, soccer
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is soccer##2
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Sport   | soccer | basketball | climbing |

